FBIS3-32318 "drlat025_a_94015" FBIS-LAT-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 February 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Assembly Rejects Talks With CIA `Sponsored' Exile Groups FL0502122694 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1200 GMT 5 Feb 94 FL0502122694 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] A communique issued by the National Assembly of the People's Government rejects as suitable spokesmen groups of Cuban exiles allegedly interested in talking with Cuban authorities but sponsored by the CIA. The document rejects, particularly, the allegedly prodialogue position of a so-called Democratic Platform abroad.
